# Implementation Plan - Multi-Language Support

The goal is to add support for **English, Hindi (with Devanagari script), Spanish, French, and Chinese**.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> This requires adding `flutter_localizations` and generating boilerplate code. I will assume standard Flutter localization best practices (ARB files).

## Proposed Changes

### Configuration
#### [MODIFY] [pubspec.yaml](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/pubspec.yaml)
- Add `flutter_localizations` and `intl`.
- Enable `generate: true`.

#### [NEW] [l10n.yaml](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/l10n.yaml)
- Configure ARB directory (`lib/l10n`) and template file.

### Localization Files
