#### [NEW] `lib/l10n/app_hi.arb` (Hindi)
#### [NEW] `lib/l10n/app_es.arb` (Spanish)
#### [NEW] `lib/l10n/app_fr.arb` (French)
#### [NEW] `lib/l10n/app_zh.arb` (Chinese)
