## Verification Plan
### Manual Verification
- Go to Settings -> Change Language to Hindi.
- Verify text changes to Hindi characters (e.g., "नमस्ते").
- Verify Chinese characters appear correctly.
- Check layout for text overflow involves longer languages (e.g., French/Spanish).
